{"tid":2408584,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"恭喜 BLACKPINK！第十支破五億 MV 誕生——〈Ice Cream〉","createTime":"2021-02-15T05:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:00:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7fff047e415495aec9f721405652e56cb6f16f","tid":2408584,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_e0ddcc4f74dbb1fc5f07d93f0b037ab6/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-15/133688-897003.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_e0ddcc4f74dbb1fc5f07d93f0b037ab6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-15%2F133688-897003.png&h=5c045cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n公開還不到 200 天，BLACKPINK 的 &ldquo;Ice Cream&rdquo; 就已成為破五億 MV 了！<br />\n<br />\n在今天（15 日）上午約 10 點時，BLACKPINK 的 &ldquo;Ice Cream&rdquo; 官方 MV 觀看次數跨越了五億次門檻，成為繼 &ldquo;DDU-DU DDU-DU&rdquo;、&ldquo;Kill This Love&rdquo;、&ldquo;BOOMBAYAH&rdquo;⋯⋯等歌曲後第十支破五億的 MV。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f11cd386ee859e0d03385a490ec16470/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-15/133688-896998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f11cd386ee859e0d03385a490ec16470%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-15%2F133688-896998.jpg&h=01882a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與 Selena Gomez 合作的 &ldquo;Ice Cream&rdquo; 於去年 8 月底問世，是 BLACKPINK 首張正規專輯〈THE ALBUM〉的第二首先行曲。配合盛夏時分發表的這首歌從旋律到 MV 都充滿清涼、繽紛的元素，加上是 BLACKPINK 久違地嘗試的可愛路線，當初一推出就大受歡迎，還在告示牌百大單曲榜上寫下韓國女團的最高名次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vRXZj0DzXIA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvRXZj0DzXIA&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=8d2e51a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vRXZj0DzXIA</a><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，&ldquo;Ice Cream&rdquo; 也登上 iTunes 國際榜、Spotify 國際榜（前 40 名）、美國榜（前 50 ）、英國官方排行榜單曲榜（前 40 名）⋯⋯等，成績斐然。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"ab90b93b7fcede4890f4b60ba80f522ab53c2e52","tid":2408584,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"太強了...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b26dc31b957836c19830d0efdb15859e85ed74","tid":2408584,"uid":255310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"都話Blackpink 2021會大發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14376e4fca56378c73d3156c9732fc38c69a4071","tid":2408584,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab90b93b7fcede4890f4b60ba80f522ab53c2e52","tid":2408584,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"太強了...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:43:47.000Z","msg":"太易玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178f1917f748e4d333769de027b8fb0142bdc7e7","tid":2408584,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"37b26dc31b957836c19830d0efdb15859e85ed74","tid":2408584,"uid":255310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"都話Blackpink 2021會大發<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"世二<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61078a40057c56142f215fe9bcd49508d1a7fd83","tid":2408584,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:12:50.000Z","msg":"我老婆&gt;黑粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399a5bf1b60aae875990089365dfbd8